te><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18575795_298456640603383_1169144119_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F18575795_298456640603383_1169144119_o.jpg&h=fabfcfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nX-mini Supa 細細部  但theater mode surround好勁<br />\n先至$1,380左右<br />\n又係咪可以充當surround speakers?</blockquote><br />\n我用Yamaha nx n500聽歌，razer leviathan 打機</blockquote><br />\n舊subwoofer咁阻掟<br />\n你放邊</blockquote><br />\n電腦枱既右下角 主機隔離 左邊仲夠位放腳踏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會無咁好<br />\n<br />\n有D高人又話  &quot;Subwoofer？傻仔！梗係放正中啦！！Blablabla.......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但現代簡約書房  點放正中subwoofer<br />\n<br />\n放枱角又畀人笑</blockquote><br />\n睇咁多本地同外國開箱/評測youtube 頻道都無聽過一定放正中 請問係邊到睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果你咁多環境同外觀問題 咁不如買耳機算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，你可能岩<br />\n耳機易D去到7.1 surround，個價錢亦低D<br />\n當然，headset =/= speakers，功能都唔同，我都明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSo far我睇左一大堆本地/外國推介，<br />\n我有以下2個心水︰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>如果買Speakers</ins></strong><br />\n如果平平地玩 5.1/7.1 Surround (virtual都OK)，<br />\n<strong>Razer Leviathan</strong>，預返$1500左右，5.1 Dolby，<br />\n1條soundbar + 1舊subwoofer (唔叫太巨大，睇返都叫接受到)<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.razerzone.com/eeimages/leviathan/img/gallery/gallery-03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.razerzone.com%2Feeimages%2Fleviathan%2Fimg%2Fgallery%2Fgallery-03.jpg&h=c6f23336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLogitech X-540本來更好聲，但全部用線接駁D 喇叭非常煩  不適合家居  不了<br />\n<br />\n7.1就不了，多數近萬元，好難搞<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>如果買Headset</ins></strong><br />\n攻頂，<br />\n<strong>Asus ROG Centurion 7.1</strong><br />\nTrue 7.1，<br />\n係重左D，<br />\n但音質有相當好評價<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.overclock3d.net/gfx/articles/2016/09/16105352578l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.overclock3d.net%2Fgfx%2Farticles%2F2016%2F09%2F16105352578l.jpg&h=854f82ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書房打機既話，以上2個選揀得唔得？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地點睇？</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.searchome.net/article/wikiPhoto/thumb/f/f7/Room049.jpg/500px-Room049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.searchome.net%2Farticle%2FwikiPhoto%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff7%2FRoom049.jpg%2F500px-Room049.jpg&h=df738a68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95f64bc7b45ca252d3b7561dd35d8467f2ec8bab","tid":340821,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用bose companion 5 打機<br />\nvirtual 5.1 個subwoofer  槍聲彭彭聲 衣櫃都震到出聲<br />\n但係唔係個種好假的bass 唔知點講清楚</blockquote><br />\nc5 大陸/外國好多論壇都話算係hi end枱面多媒體音箱</blockquote><br />\n個人覺得Bose companion 5係個左右speaker唔太好睇<br />\n<br />\n不過無錯  佢算係幾多好評"},{"pid":"f1b1223b4fd0ab49794be9d9f02e52acb9a2efcd","tid":340821,"uid":53248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"聽歌多打機少<br />\n3000筆直有乜推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.1 或者 2.0都OK"},{"pid":"8b57b904b57b0ce99fa58c8cf57a7719ea95c804","tid":340821,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽歌多打機少<br />\n3000筆直有乜推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.1 或者 2.0都OK</blockquote><br />\n隔離post問吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff919ad2bf9cd7d8f143381ad215c8e56b6bba4e","tid":340821,"uid":22817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18575795_298456640603383_1169144119_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail